        "description": "# TOXI Media - Immersive VR Experiences\n\nDiscover a world of immersive VR with TOXI Media's app, featuring a diverse collection of experiences that blend art, technology, and storytelling.\n\n- **Patent Quest**: An arcade-style game that challenges your strategic thinking as you navigate the world of innovation and intellectual property.\n  \n- **After You're Gone**: Immerse yourself in a live jazz performance by the Fancy Dogs™, where every note surrounds you in a rich musical atmosphere.\n  \n- **Viaje**: Embark on an auditory journey crafted by Fermín Delía, where sound and emotion guide you through a surreal, introspective landscape.\n  \n- **Juana La Loca**: Explore the emotional depths of Spain's enigmatic queen in this immersive installation by Ana Arzoumanian.\n  \n- **Descubriendo BA con Luz**: Take a rainy stroll through Buenos Aires' Recoleta neighborhood, discovering its history and culture in a unique, atmospheric tour.\n  \n- **Torta**: Enter the vibrant world of Mariana César’s art, where each piece comes alive in a dynamic, interactive environment.\n\nDownload the TOXI Media app to explore these captivating VR experiences and discover new perspectives through immersive storytelling.\n",
